lead_paragraph: Bart Bryant birdied his last two holes for a six-under-par 65 and a one-shot lead among early starters who were able to beat the rain at the PODS Championship in Palm Harbor, Fla. Ernie Els, coming off a victory in the Honda Classic that ended an 0-for-47 drought on the PGA Tour, was part of the afternoon starters who did not finish.
